Invocation Name: relaxing white noise
des:
Relaxing White Noise is a proven and effective way to block out distractions and fall asleep easy. This special white noise has its frequencies slightly muted to provide a more relaxing tone for sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Relaxing White Noise, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
